---
---

<section class="rule-section" id="about" aria-labelledby="rule-heading">
  <div class="container rule-section__inner">
    <div class="rule-content reveal-left">
      <p class="section-tag">THE FLORIDA 25% RULE</p>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="rule-heading">Repair or Replace?<br/>We'll Tell You the Truth.</h2>
      <p class="rule-content__body">
        Florida's 2014 Building Code states: if more than <strong>25% of your roof</strong> is repaired or replaced in a 12-month period, the entire roofing system must be brought up to current code — which usually means a full replacement.
      </p>
      <p class="rule-content__body">
        At Affordable Roofing Systems, our Master Elite inspectors will give you an <strong>honest, line-by-line assessment</strong> so you always know exactly what makes the most financial sense for your home — no upselling, no scare tactics.
      </p>
      <div class="rule-content__badges">
        <div class="mini-badge">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          100% Honest Inspection
        </div>
        <div class="mini-badge">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          No Hidden Fees
        </div>
        <div class="mini-badge">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
          Same-Day Estimates
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="align-self: flex-start; margin-top: 8px;">Schedule Free Inspection</a>
    </div>

    <div class="rule-image reveal-right">
      <img
        src="/images/roof-inspection.jpg"
        alt="Professional roof inspection in Tampa, Florida"
        loading="lazy"
        width="620"
        height="480"
      />
      <div class="rule-image__card">
        <div class="rule-image__card-num">25<span>%</span></div>
        <div class="rule-image__card-text">Florida Rule Threshold — we'll measure yours for free</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.rule-section {
  background: var(--bg-secondary);
  padding: 100px 0;
}
.rule-section__inner {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 80px;
}

/* Content side */
.rule-content {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 20px;
}
.rule-content .section-title {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}
.rule-content__body {
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.75;
}
.rule-content__body strong { color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 700; }

.rule-content__badges {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 12px;
  margin: 8px 0;
}
.mini-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  background: white;
  border: 1px solid #dde2eb;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  padding: 8px 16px;
  font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--navy);
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
}
.mini-badge svg { color: var(--orange); flex-shrink: 0; }

/* Image side */
.rule-image {
  flex: 0 0 560px;
  position: relative;
}
.rule-image img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 480px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(26,61,110,0.2);
}

.rule-image__card {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -24px;
  left: -24px;
  background: var(--navy);
  color: white;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  padding: 24px 28px;
  box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(26,61,110,0.3);
  max-width: 220px;
  animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}
.rule-image__card-num {
  font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: 3rem;
  color: var(--orange);
  line-height: 1;
}
.rule-image__card-num span { font-size: 2rem; }
.rule-image__card-text {
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  opacity: 0.8;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-top: 8px;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .rule-section__inner { gap: 48px; }
  .rule-image { flex: 0 0 420px; }
}
@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .rule-section__inner { flex-direction: column; }
  .rule-image { flex: none; width: 100%; }
  .rule-image img { height: 320px; }
  .rule-image__card { bottom: -16px; left: 16px; }
}
</style>
